{"tid":1718392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察濫權報告無人承印 港印刷商自我審查","createTime":"2019-11-13T23:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:32:29.000Z","uid":125168,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc40fec68e6a91bf572a9c163bfb5e41a22d245","tid":1718392,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:56:54.000Z","msg":"【警察濫權報告無人承印｜作者：港印刷商自我審查 - 本土新聞】<br />\n<br />\n一群網民自發編寫的《香港警隊的法定權力及監管：調查報告書》已在網上推出公眾試閱版，最新英文版本包括直至十月二日的警隊涉嫌濫權資料。<br />\n<br />\n該報告的一名作者在臉書稱，他們一直想將報告重新排版、設計封面、除錯，再印刷派發給重要人士、團體與機構。然而報告印刷進度受阻，他們暫時未找到一間香港公司肯幫忙承印，即使一些「比較黃」的公司亦聲稱：「太牽涉政治嘅嘢暫時唔印住。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2019/11/hkpf-report/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2019%2F11%2Fhkpf-report%2F&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=ae36ee17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2019/11/hkpf-report/</a>"},{"pid":"7075df252b8571df5bbcfe5e8d60333addadd4f0","tid":1718392,"uid":212646,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:00:43.000Z","msg":"拎去台灣印<br />\n有無file?我搞"},{"pid":"0c8a9054c6ba34a58419ad621f3a136bedc36571","tid":1718392,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:01:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8de5ecc7197c05bfe37304ade795d0c85119059f","tid":1718392,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7075df252b8571df5bbcfe5e8d60333addadd4f0","tid":1718392,"uid":212646,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:00:43.000Z","msg":"拎去台灣印<br />\n有無file?我搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:02:46.000Z","msg":"考慮埋印完用咩方法入境"},{"pid":"3e2f64139356bfbfcec54bcb45e380960c8e5686","tid":1718392,"uid":271123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7075df252b8571df5bbcfe5e8d60333addadd4f0","tid":1718392,"uid":212646,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:00:43.000Z","msg":"拎去台灣印<br />\n有無file?我搞"},"citedBy"